Uses of Package
Window

  • Packages that use Window 
    Package Description
    Main
    This package contains classes to provide application launch methods.
    Window
    Classes and interfaces found in this package are designed to implement the pages and main functionalities of the application.
  • Classes in Window used by Main 
    Class and Description
    IStorage
    Contains method specifications of data component of application.
  • Classes in Window used by Window 
    Class and Description
    IContainer
    Contains method specifications of controller component of application.
    IInfoPage 
    IIntroPage
    Contains method specifications of introduction page of application.
    IPlayPage
    Contains method specifications of play page of application.
    ISettingsPage
    Contains method specifications of settings page of application.
    IStorage
    Contains method specifications of data component of application.
    IStorage.IBoardModeItem
    This sub-interface of IStorage contains method specifications of settings of a board mode option.
    IStorage.IBoardModeItem.IPlayerRow
    This sub-interface of IStorage contains method specifications of player data representation.
    JFXPage
    Contains JavaFX specific implementations of TPage abstract class.
    TSelectItem
    Extended implementation of IItem used typically in select box graphical components.
